### Teste da API - AI Chat Backend

### 1. Criar usuário admin
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin User",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "admin"
}

### 2. Fazer login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. Testar endpoint protegido (substitua <token> pelo token retornado)
GET http://localhost:3000/users
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 4. Testar chat
POST http://localhost:3000/chat
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Explique o que é TypeScript"
}

### 5. Listar chats
GET http://localhost:3000/chat
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 6. Testar OpenAI direto (ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:3000/openai/chat
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Explique o que é NestJS"
} 